Package: kdeutils3
Version: 3.0.2
Revision: 1
Depends: kdelibs3 (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdelibs3-ssl (>= 3.0.2-1), kdebase3 (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdebase3-ssl (>= 3.0.2-1), efax
BuildDepends: kdelibs3-dev (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdelibs3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.2-1), kdebase3-dev (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdebase3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.2-1), automake15, autoconf25, libtool14, fink (>= 0.9.12)
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Source: http://download.kde.org/stable/%v/src/kdeutils-%v.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: 285a7efd9e3379e823bf36ca4c839b5e
PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/%f.patch | patch -p0
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib
SetCPPFLAGS: -no-cpp-precomp
SetCFLAGS: -fno-common
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p --with-qt-dir=%p --with-extra-libs=%p/lib --with-extra-includes=%p/include --enable-mt --with-pic --enable-rpath --enable-shared=yes --enable-static=yes --mandir=%i/share/man --with-xinerama --enable-final $KDEOPTS
CompileScript: <<
 make -f Makefile.cvs
 (export KDEDIR=%p; sh configure %c; make)
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make install DESTDIR=%d
<<
Splitoff: <<
 Package: %N-dev
 Description: Development libraries and headers for KDE utils
 Depends: %N (= %v-%r)
 Suggests: kdebase3-dev (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdebase3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.2-1)
 BuildDependsOnly: true
 Files: include/ lib/*.a lib/kde3/*.a lib/kde3/kcharselectapplet.so lib/libark.so
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING INSTALL README
Description: KDE - Misc. utilities
DescDetail: <<
  Various miscellaneous utilities for KDE.
<<
DescPort: <<
Nothing special needed other than the admin/ patch from kdebase and
a few changes to Makefile.am's.

NOTE: KDE packages do *not* have an -shlibs because of KDE's use of  
libltdl!  The .la's *must* be used in conjunction with the dynamic
libraries, and they are unversioned filenames, so multiple -shlibs would
conflict.
<<
